headline: Kimberly-Clark (KMB) Up 5.8% Since Last Earnings Report: Can It Continue?
summary: Kimberly-Clark (KMB) reported earnings 30 days ago. What's next for the stock? We take a look at earnings estimates for some clues.

headline: Kimberly-Clark Foundation Awards 30 Bright Futures Scholarships to High School Seniors
summary: Kimberly-Clark today announced the recipients of its Bright Futures college scholarships, awarding 30 high school seniors from across North America. These students, children of Kimberly-Clark employees, were selected based on their academic achievements, leadership qualities, work experience, and extracurricular activities.
